name: Chez Bisma
address: Br.Lantangkatik, Telaga Tawang, Kec. Sidemen, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80864, Indonesia
review 1: the rooms are nice and comfortable, the surroundings are very quiet plus the sounds of nature. friendly service, strategic location if you want to go to other sidemen areas.
review 2:
I just spent a night here before a trail run (there is some magical scenery within walking distance of Chez Bisma) and was pleasantly surprised at how clean, spacious and quiet the room was (I'm quite picky when it comes to cleanliness). Loved the outdoor shower with view of the surrounding forest and stars at night. The family was very welcoming and made me feel at home. It's a humble spot that's perfect for some peace and quiet in Sidemen's countryside.
Would definitely come back here!
review 3:
A lovely place to stay and the host family members are delightful. Excellent value.
The rooms are quite new and very clean.
The indoor/outdoor bathrooms are special, particularly the shower.
Breakfast is included and other delicious meals are available
review 4:
Very nice accommodations!
The owner and his family is very sweet and helpful. You can rent scooter with helmet, he can drive you in the car, he have many good suggestions for what to do in the area. The breakfast is simple and very tasteful, and you can order lunch and dinner, which is nice if you just want to relax in the amazing surroundings.
review 5:
We only stayed for one night but this is a place you can easily spend a couple. The family is so nice and we had dinner as well which we would really recommend. The room was perfect and from our outside shower we looked directly into the jungleâ€¦ simply lovely!

Thanks again for having us.
